snippet.title: Best VGM 1164 - Return All Robots! - Fantastic Robotique
snippet.description:
Get the album @ http://zirconstudios.bandcamp.com/album/return-all-robots-original-soundtrack

Best VGM 1407 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=deKo_UHZa14

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PC
Return All Robots! (2010)
Fantastic Robotique
